//One node per line
// Line starting with // are comments, must be ignored
// Line starting with - or + are actual nodes
// Line starting with => are redirection to a node
// If there are multiple redirections in a line, we try the first one and if this node has already been visited, we go to the second, etc.
// Right after -, + or =>, there is the unique id of the node
// Right after the id, there is the score given by this node when visited
